  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ensure girls stay in school every day of the month</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Poverty affects schooling of 7 Million SA girls who miss up to 40 days a year of school   because they cannot afford sanitary pads.   There are many expensive solutions, the simplest and cheapest one of all is to distribute packets of pads, 12 at a time, which will see them through the year of school.  We aim to raise money to do just that so that those girls wont be embarrassed at school.   We need your help, the more we manage to buy, the more girls we can help</narrative>
  </description>
